All vegetables and unsaturated fat sources such as avocado, olives and most
nuts and seeds are great for the heart so we’ve thrown a few ingredients
together with a dressing made with macadamia nut oil (you can swap this for
extra virgin olive oil) and balsamic vinegar, to show some love to your heart!
Serve it as a side salad to some heart healthy fish like salmon.
